OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FIt comes as recent Government figures
OL,8,Frevealed that the number of pupils
OL,9,Fclassed as "severely absent" in
OL,10,FEngland reached a record high last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FDepartment for Education (DfE) data
OL,14,Flast week found that the number of
OL,15,Funauthorised pupil absences from
OL,16,Fschools in England increased last year.
