OL,7,FIt has called on school leaders to
OL,8,Fwork closely with parents to
OL,9,Funderstand the barriers to attendance.
OL,10,FThis could include workshops and home
OL,11,Fvisits.
OL,13,FThe NFER has also called on
OL,14,Fpolicymakers to increase funding for
OL,15,Fattendance and pastoral support to
OL,16,Fhelp schools.
