OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FMatt Walker, NFER senior research
OL,8,Fmanager and co-author of the report,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Attendance is strongly linked
OL,10,Fto educational outcomes, so it's
OL,11,Fconcerning that absence rates remain
OL,12,Fhigh.
OL,14,F"The study responses suggest schools
OL,15,Fshould consider prioritising
OL,16,Fencouraging and individualised
OL,17,Fapproaches in addition to punitive
OL,18,Fsanctions."
