OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHe added: "There needs to be a
OL,8,Fstrategic response from the government
OL,9,Fto the growing problem of pupil
OL,10,Fabsence, and schools must be provided
OL,11,Fwith the tools they need to tackle
OL,12,Fthis."
OL,14,FPaul Whiteman, general secretary at
OL,15,Fschool leaders' union NAHT, said:
OL,16,F"These findings echo what school
OL,17,Fleaders tell us about the severe
OL,18,Flimitations of parental fines in
OL,19,Fimproving pupil attendance.
