OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Absence most often reflects issues
OL,8,Fbeyond the school gate, like mental
OL,9,Fhealth challenges and poverty, and
OL,10,Fclearly identifying and being able to
OL,11,Fsupport families to address these
OL,12,Fissues is far more effective."
OL,14,FHe added: "If the link between absence
OL,15,Fand term-time holidays is to be
OL,16,Fbroken, the only sustainable solution
OL,17,Fis government action to prevent travel
OL,18,Ffirms unfairly hiking prices during
OL,19,Fschool holidays."
